Start program
    Setup signal listener for exit (ctrl + c)
    Parse args
        if -f then go to Read From File Loop
        if none then go to Generate Words Loop

Read From File Loop
    Open file
        if error then exit
    Check for EOF
        If EOF then exit
    loop
        Read MAX_SIZE bytes from file into memory
        Display target line
        Read input until end of target line
        Display stats
    EXIT

Generate Words Loop
    Loop
        Generate target line using words.txt
        Display target line
        Read input until end of target line
        Display stats
    If ctrl+c then EXIT
